  "time_ut": 1657350292,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb2\u0bcd, \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "In front of the President's House, the protestors seized a vehicle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Heavy security was beefed up on the roads leading to the Presidential Palace. Many obstacles were put up.",
        "All the barriers were broken by the demonstrators. The police resorted to tear gas and water cannons without breaking down the barricades.",
        "However, the protesters broke through the barricades and reached the main gate of the Presidential Palace via Saddam Street. The demonstration is being carried out in front of that gate.",
        "In addition, they have also seized the water utility vehicle of the police. Some protesters climbed on top of the vehicle."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "House",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
      ],
